ata-gramm="false"><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Repair and rejuvenate for Autumn</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1711459472170" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1711459472170"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-justify-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p>Autumn is an ideal time to focus on repairing any summer-induced skin damage. As summer fades, your skin might reveal sun-induced blemishes.  Autumn presents the ideal chance for renewal. Enter antioxidants, with<a href="https://www.koreanskincare.co.uk/collections/vitamin-c" class=""> Vitamin C</a> in the spotlight. This powerhouse ingredient not only fades sunspots but also <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">stimulates collagen production, rejuvenating your skin for that youthful allure</span>.</p><p><br></p><p>Elevate your routine with Vitamin C-infused products, from serums to moisturizers, and unveil a revitalized complexion. Let this autumn mark not only nature's transformation but also your skin's radiant revival, courtesy of antioxidants like Vitamin C.</p><p></p><p></p><p