"e-1711459472287" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1711459472287"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-justify-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">Just as you swap out your lightweight summer wardrobe for cozy sweaters, it's time to switch up your moisturizer too. Reach for richer, creamier formulas while picking your moisturizer. As the temperature drops, your skin craves deep nourishment. Ingredients like Shea Butter and natural oils work wonders in providing that extra dose of hydration your skin craves during the cooler months.</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><strong>Pyunkang Yul - ATO Cream Blue Label</strong></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">The Pyunkang Yul <a href="/products/pyunkang-yul-ato-cream-blue-label?variant=33359822618687" class="" style="text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" data-position="3">ATO Cream Blue Label</a> stands as a guardian of skin hydration, <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">forging an unbreakable shield against dryness and discomfort. Enthroned at the heart of its formulation is the revered Honeysuckle Flower Extract, a resilient survivor of even the harshest weathers, now extending its calming embrace to shield the skin from the tempests of external stress. Shea Butter and Ceramide are also present to help strengthen, moisturize, and revitalize the skin.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><strong style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I'm From - Rice Cream</strong></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The next product up is the I’m From <a href="/products/im-from-rice-cream?variant=39890226380863" class="" style="text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" data-position="4">Rice Cream</a> - a luminous ode to vegan hydration. Formulated with 41% Rice Bran Ceramide, it effectively controls sebum, locks in moisture, and strengthens skin, producing a revitalized glow. This cream has a silky texture that melts instantly into the skin.</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><strong style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">SKIN&LAB - Barrierderm Intensive Cream</strong></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Last but not least, we have a highly effecive cream by SKIN&LAB <a href="/products/copy-of-barrierderm-intensive-cream-50ml?variant=47334159909213" class="" style="text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(10, 10, 10);" data-position="5">Barrierderm Intensive Cream</a>. It empowers your natural barrier, combatting dryne